:0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T14:54:46.000Z","msg":"幫手推 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33bf47dc8eb5564d5c558f0985b7d270a8527603","tid":117111,"uid":72948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T23:10:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/31/152216_de2357405a75b91883bf1cf8788c8bb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F31%2F152216_de2357405a75b91883bf1cf8788c8bb1.jpg&h=31435ace&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b03d053851e5f7587a032516bc831fe6c78b88b3","tid":117111,"uid":68098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T23:22:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我隊Band最近諗緊一個問題，如果我地想租自己地方燈油火蠟加埋Gear加埋租要幾多錢。<br />\n所以想問下各大連登Band仔，聽下你地嘅經驗，係邊租好，邊到搵單位諸如此類啦。<br />\n其實講下你地夾Band啲野都得，志在交流下心得。</blockquote><br />\n三千至四千左右但好細<br />\n150呎至250左右<br />\n<br />\n三個月按一個月上期<br />\n電費按金1000<br />\n如果揾地産要比多半個月佢做佣<br />\n<br />\n你要有Set 鼓 二手2500-4000<br />\nmixer with speakers 二手 三千左右<br />\nbass amp around 4000<br />\nguitar amp 二手 約 2500起<br />\n<br />\n隔音綿 淘 約$3 塊<br />\n<br />\n淨係租金 頭炮$17000<br />\n架生(約數）$13000<br />\n綿 $1000<br />\n<br />\n每月租4000<br />\n電約$500-$800"},{"pid":"bcfe831e019d9358e019dad3a4631b6236b7953f","tid":117111,"uid":22206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T23:49:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>觀塘同葵涌都有間band房，支出差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尤其電費</blockquote><br />\n差幾遠"},{"pid":"6d0d5b9e111c3e18b40b3d1285062043ac856065","tid":117111,"uid":80527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T02:15:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>觀塘同葵涌都有間band房，支出差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尤其電費</blockquote><br />\n差幾遠</blockquote><br />\n電費觀塘千幾一個月，葵涌幾十蚊一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 燈用LED會比較慳電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7033e8deed1dfa7f2855e723ae27bc7ea3b931ad","tid":117111,"uid":22206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T07:31:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>觀塘同葵涌都有間band房，支出差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尤其電費</blockquote><br />\n差幾遠</blockquote><br />\n電費觀塘千幾一個月，葵涌幾十蚊一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 燈用LED會比較慳電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌差咁撚遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所有bandMate都係九龍人真係想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af218d4ea4c092c27b34c0f8482b4a911c63497d","tid":117111,"uid":73404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T08:00:18.000Z","msg":"唔好講租 淨係講setup<br />\n買amp買鼓買咪買mixer..<br />\n就算當你全部都買二手 加埋都成皮幾野 <br />\n已經assume左唔洗裝修唔計按金<br />\n講真 去旺角租番幾個鐘無咁嬲啦 好多都開到好夜<br />\n要作歌既 咪搵個位傾好 諗定有咩要試 上到去逐樣執<br />\n要錄音既 其實有個interface有部電腦都錄到呢 最多比你加支mic加個preamp 求其搵間房都做到"},{"pid":"9f8c15f5c1465418d3ffba4fbda5cde6c59bd204","tid":117111,"uid":6504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T09:45:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好講租 淨係講setup<br />\n買amp買鼓買咪買mixer..<br />\n就算當你全部都買二手 加埋都成皮幾野 <br />\n已經assume左唔洗裝修唔計按金<br />\n講真 去旺角租番幾個鐘無咁嬲啦 好多都開到好夜<br />\n要作歌既 咪搵個位傾好 諗定有咩要試 上到去逐樣執<br />\n要錄音既 其實有個interface有部電腦都錄到呢 最多比你加支mic加個preamp 求其搵間房都做到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n皮幾野我怕唔得<br />\n我果邊幾條友夾<br />\n二按一上，加埋隔音綿同裝修料，連埋熱水爐雪櫃樂器電腦諸如此類，要三皮起手<br />\n<br />\n牛頭角"},{"pid":"bd1162e1b2974ef9a7975f9aeee76d3fcc482e6e","tid":117111,"uid":22206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T10:13:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔好講租 淨係講setup<br />\n買amp買鼓買咪買mixer..<br />\n就算當你全部都買二手 加埋都成